title: VA -GSTS:Tavern Brawls: G & H compilations
description:
I know you guys have just been dying to grab this next and latest compilation release from www.gststracker.com This next great part of the brilliant GSTS compilation of Tavern Brawls and Uppercuts is here eagarly awaiting you!! 
The "H" component is rife with rich, amazing music from some of the best H bands in our favoured genres....so grab it while you can, and then race over to www.gststracker.com for the equally exciting and masterful "G" compilation (see below for details). While you are there, be sure to check out all the brilliant stuff on offer, and meet our awesome community!!
